Description: Teleport to the entrance of a Mists of Pandaria dungeon for which you have earned a Gold medal. The cooldown of these spells will reset when you complete any challenge mode.

Description: Alternate cosmetic variants of Polymorph, which transform your target into a variety of creatures.

Description: Modify your ranged weapon to use exotic munitions.

Name: Warlord's Path
Description: Teleport to the entrance of a Warlords of Draenor dungeon for which you have earned a Gold medal. The cooldown of these spells will reset when you complete any challenge mode.

Name: Pet Utility
Description: A variety of tools to help you manage your pet.

Name: Hex Variants
Description: Alternate cosmetic variants of Hex, which transform your target into a variety of creatures.

Name: Kyrian Instruments
Description: Play an instrument of the Kyrian.

Name: Hero's Path: Shadowlands
Description: Teleport to the entrance of a Shadowlands Dungeon for which you have earned the Keystone Hero achievement. The cooldown of these spells will reset when you complete a Mythic Keystone Dungeon.
